Hello! Welcome to your potion shop! You are making potions for customers who want potions a very specific way.
They'll order either a Health, Mana or Stamina potion first. Click the red Health fruit to make a health potion, the blue Mana fruit to make a Mana potion, or the green Stamina fruit to make a Stamina potion!
Then they'll specify the exact flavor they want, in combinations of Sweet, Sour and Bitter! They're very vague about it, so it's up to you to figure out what they mean.
Click and hold on the purple grapes here to make the potion sweet, the green grapes make your potion sour, and the white grapes make your potion bitter!
Once it's full, you can click on the cauldron and your customer will let you know how much they like their potion. This will update your star rating, try to get five stars!
If you need a visual guide for your cauldron, click the eye button, and if you need to restart your potion click the trash button.
Good luck!
